name: Voxo Studio
description:
Welcome to the Voxo Studio!


Here we will be adding graphic templates and assets that the community can use.


Please feel free to reach out to @Sherin in Discord (discord.gg/voxodeus) for any questions, requests or feedback.


* * *


VoxoDeus is the first large-scale, interactive, 3D NFT collectible comprising of 6,313 unique, scifi-mythic creatures, ranging from sentient robots to immortal cosmic beings.


3D interactivity, swappable backgrounds, ambient music, and also the first NFT project to partner with @TheSandboxGame to create playable avatars for VoxoDeus NFT owners.


Join our incredible Discord & Twitter community for live updates, and head over to OpenSea to mint our remaining Voxos.


-------- voxodeus.io
